<p>Shouldn't the form component be throwing a huge error about that?</p>
<h2 id="the-by-reference-form-option">The by_reference Form Option <a class="headerlink" href="by-reference-adder-remover#the-by-reference-form-option" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>In theory... yes! But, the form is being <em>really</em> sneaky. Remember, the <code>studiedGenuses</code>
property is an <code>ArrayCollection</code> object:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="fcd778db36">
    <div class="meta">
