<p>After that, add the remover: <code>public function removeStudiedGenus()</code> also with a
<code>Genus</code> argument. In here, say <code>$this-&gt;studiedGenuses-&gt;removeElement($genus)</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="066ee22ffc">
